### Test API Endpoints
### Make sure the backend server is running on http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### ========== AUTH ENDPOINTS ==========

### 1. Sign Up
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### 2. Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Get Profile (Replace TOKEN with your JWT token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN


### ========== EVENT ENDPOINTS ==========

### 4. Create Event (Replace TOKEN with your JWT token)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "title": "Team Meeting",
  "startTime": "2024-11-15T10:00",
  "endTime": "2024-11-15T11:00",
  "status": "BUSY"
}

### 5. Get All Events (Replace TOKEN with your JWT token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/events
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### 6. Get Event by ID (Replace TOKEN and EVENT_ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/events/EVENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### 7. Update Event (Replace TOKEN and EVENT_ID)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/events/EVENT_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "title": "Updated Meeting",
  "status": "SWAPPABLE"
}

### 8. Delete Event (Replace TOKEN and EVENT_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/events/EVENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN


### ========== SWAP ENDPOINTS ==========

### 9. Get Swappable Slots (Replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/swappable-slots
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### 10. Create Swap Request (Replace TOKEN, MY_SLOT_ID, THEIR_SLOT_ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/swap-request
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "mySlotId": "MY_SLOT_ID",
  "theirSlotId": "THEIR_SLOT_ID"
}

### 11. Get Incoming Swap Requests (Replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/swap-requests/incoming
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### 12. Get Outgoing Swap Requests (Replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/swap-requests/outgoing
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### 13. Accept Swap Request (Replace TOKEN and REQUEST_ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/swap-response/REQUEST_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "accept": true
}

### 14. Reject Swap Request (Replace TOKEN and REQUEST_ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/swap-response/REQUEST_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "accept": false
}
